description: Recently sold: $360,000. Gorgeous newly updated rambler in Friendly Hills neighborhood. Recently sold: $210,000. Come see this well maintained, tucked away 2 Bedroom and 2 bathroom townhome in Mendota Heights with close proximity to 494 and 35E. The home comes with a 1 year home warranty and includes a complimentary re-key service to ensure you will have an easy transition. Stay warm this winter with the newly installed furnace, thermostat, and windows while enjoying many nicely done upgrades that range from new carpeting and flooring throughout, to recently upgraded cabinets and hardware in both bathrooms. The home features newer light fixtures and an upgraded kitchen with granite countertops and newer SS refrigerator and oven. The home also has been professionally deep cleaned. Just move-in and enjoy a book in the upstairs loft area. With such close proximity to shops, parks and schools this is truly Mendota Heights living at its finest.

description: Recently sold: $548,000. Custom 4 BR/4BA Rambler on a private corner lot. Fully updated with a spacious open-concept kitchen/DR/LR. Sunken LR features a immaculate brick wood burning FP & vaulted ceilings. The huge kitchen has custom cabinets & granite countertops with newer stainless steel appliances. The center island & coffee bar open to the DR that overlooks the private patio. Main level master suite with sitting room, walk-in closets & an updated ceramic private BA with separate shower & air jet tub. Lower level offers 3 additional BR & 2 BA, a fully equipped bar kitchen with custom bar top & spacious FR with stone wood burning FP. Beautifully maintained landscaping help keep the yard private so you can enjoy the small pond & bonfire patio. Attached & insulated 2 stall garage.

Recently sold: $515,000. 4 BD, 3 BA light-filled ranch walkout with vaulted ceiling and open floor plan; remodel in 2013-14. Anderson windows throughout (with exception of two brand new Pella windows). 

On the main level: new bright kitchen with quartz counter tops and newer appliances that flow into dining room and living area with newer modern gas fireplace, 4-season porch used as office/playroom with deck stairs leading to private backyard, new exterior doors, new light fixtures and hardware, newer mudroom/locker-system for snow clothes and boots, 3 bedrooms with master 3/4 bath and separate main floor bath, and all new paint throughout. 

On lower level: large family room with gas fireplace and walkout to private backyard, movie theater with dry-bar and drink refrigerator, 1 large bedroom and bath, laundry room with newer over-sized front loading washer/dryer and folding counter space, and unfinished utility room with high-efficiency furnace and air exchanger and plenty of storage space.
